  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nWhenever injecting a spy by `@InjectSpy Service service` the service's @PostConstruct method is executed.\r\nWould be nice to have a flag like `@InjectSpy(skipPostConstruct=true)` or nicer.\r\nWithout changing productioin code/config, this can be AFAIK only achieved by creating the spy by `Mockito.spy(Service.class)` which brings other problems (injected fields in Service are null).\r\n\r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\n_No response_",
